Geislingen: More than 100 young Catholics of the small hay mountain strengthen in the Firmung its creed
In two religious services, 101,15- and 16-year-old youth of the Seelsorgeeinheit became at the small hay mountain gefirmt.
The religious service accompanied at the morning the group tepid date sowed, in the afternoon the youth choir The Spirit.
With the reception of the Firmsakraments, the youths said yes to its baptism and requested the power of the holy spirit.
The Firmlinge had prepared itself in the past months, under the direction of deacon of pure Dehner and the assistance of numerous parishioners for the large festival day.
In different projects, they became acquainted with at the same time different tasks of the Christian community life and experienced jointly the youth day in Untermachtal.
